headline: Does GE’s Surge Mean Opportunity After India’s $1B Engine Deal Approval?
summary: If you have been watching General Electric recently, you know the stock is never far from the headlines or the center of the market's attention. Maybe you are wondering whether now is the right time to make a decision, or if GE's momentous rise could keep going. It is a fair question, especially given how dramatically the company has transformed itself and how the market has reacted along the way. GE's shares have seen strong gains not just this year, but over the long term. Fresh off a 63.2%...
